TABLE_SELECT: MENU_TYPE TYPE,MENU_ICON ICON,MENU_INFO INFO,MENU_AREA AREA,MENU_TIP TIP,DS_MENU_FLAG MENU,MENU_TODO_FLAG TODO,DS_FOLDER_FLAG FOLDER,DS_NORMAL_FLAG NORMAL,DS_NAME DSNAME,DS_ICON DSICON,MENU_NODE_VIRTUAL VIRTUAL,MENU_TODO_TYPE ALERT,MENU_DEV_TYPES MENU_DEV_TYPES
